Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:11.66,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Daddy! Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:26.55,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:48.24,Main,Stagehand,0,0,0,,Five minutes until showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:36.70,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,A long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.87,0:01:41.83,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,...the people of Enju \N built two towers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:47.30,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,Nine-storied towers \N so tall they seemed to reach the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.38,0:01:50.05,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,The Bell Tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:53.72,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,...and the Gong Tower.{suzu, kane are both types of bells. HGSS revealed that the intended meanings were the bells instead of Tin/Brass, but kane no tou never got an official reTL...}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:02:01.77,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,One day, two Legendary Pokémon \N from far away appeared before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:04.35,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,The god of rainbows, Houou...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:17.37,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,...and the god of the sea, Lugia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:30.34,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,Houou descended \N upon the Bell Tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:36.05,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,...and Lugia \N upon the Gong Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:41.14,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,The people communed \N with those Pokémon,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:44.31,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,and before long, \N formed bonds with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:54.07,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,{\q2}And those bonds lasted until a fateful night \N 150 years ago, when moonlight shone upon the towers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:18.64,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,150 years ago, \N Lugia’s rest was {stolen away}disturbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:30.73,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,Fierce lightning, violent winds...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:34.19,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,A storm enveloped \N the city of Enju,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:37.78,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,culminating in a tremendous \N lightning bolt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:40.32,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,...which struck the Gong Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:49.46,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,Flames engulfed \N the tall tower in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:57.43,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,Before long, \N it became an inferno!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:08.06,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,Lugia ascended high into the skies \N and brought forth strong winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:13.27,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,And yet... the flames did not fade, \N only seeming to spread further...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:21.74,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,Lugia summoned rain \N to the skies above Enju.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:29.96,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,The rain fiercely \N combated the fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.21,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,...until it was \N completely quenched.{Until nothing remained.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:05.28,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,Once the dreadful night was past, \N the sun began to rise,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:09.37,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,heralding a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:16.88,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,Lugia had lost its bonds with the people, \N and with a broken heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.38,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,...it departed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:25.18,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,And now, \N deep beneath the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:27.68,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,it waits for one \N with a pure heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:30.89,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,...to this very day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.32,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,The Gong Tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:46.16,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,To remind us \N of what we have lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:49.33,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,and to never allow the same {mistake}tragedy \N to happen again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:52.58,Main,Maiko-han,0,0,0,,It remains, even now.
